cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV. 

The paper discusses a policy search method using trust-region optimization and natural gradient updates, which are commonly used in reinforcement learning and control tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also mentions experiments on continuous control tasks and partially observable tasks, which suggests cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as possible categories.
